
# House Price Prediction

## Description

This project predicts house prices based on area and number of bedrooms using machine learning.

## Dataset

* Source: Manually created
* Description: Contains house area, bedrooms, and price

## Steps Performed

1. Data Cleaning
2. Exploratory Data Analysis
3. Visualization
4. Model Building using Linear Regression

## Results

* Model successfully predicts house prices
* Mean Absolute Error calculated

## Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* Matplotlib
* Scikit-learn

## Conclusion

The project demonstrates basic machine learning techniques for prediction tasks.

